snippet.title: Squirreltopia - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
An evil robot squirrel has attacked Squirreltopia. Scurry through diverse levels like the desert, forests, factories, and alien planets. Use bubble machines, bomb-blocks, balloons, invisi-blocks, and more to save the planet and prevent squirrel extinction!

Do you have the squirrel skills to handle it?

Squirreltopia (C) Sean Davy
